name: Chong Round King Shibe (Fat Shiba Inu)
description:
ADOPT ME SERIES

Psssst woof woof bark...
 
Hey! you there! With a wonderful smile!
I'm gonna tell you something...never known to humankind.

There is no such thing as ugly, all of us are beautiful, have faith in yourself, and you’re gonna light up the world, make people feel loved!

Hey, once you're done, chill... and think about all the good memories, the bad ones are a no-no, Get rid of the stress, and don't listen to the negatives.
 
I love you,
CHONG ROUND KING SHIBE :) <3
